sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant C as CLI
    participant B as BuildManager
    participant H as Node HTTP Server
    participant FS as FileSystem

    U->>C: foundryspec serve
    C->>B: serve()
    B->>FS: Check if dist/ exists
    opt dist/ missing
        B->>B: build()
    end
    B->>H: Start Server on Port (default 3000)
    U->>H: Request index.html
    H->>FS: Read dist/index.html
    H-->>U: Documentation Hub
